---
title: Pork Sausage Linguine with parsley and pomodoro sauce
description: If you're looking for something that's filling and satisfyingly savoury then this meaty pasta dish is it. Pan-fried pork sausages are smothered in a parsley pomodoro sauce then topped off with freshly torn basil and a sharp Italian style cheese.
